367
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:53,330
Go with me!

368
00:30:53,330 --> 00:30:54,920
Mom!

369
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:56,760
I…

370
00:31:06,820 --> 00:31:10,029
Jiang Jing. Jiang Jing.

371
00:31:24,490 --> 00:31:26,830
